featured_reviews.review_translated_text:
*_Assalamu Alaikum Warhamtullahi Wabarakatuhu_*

*18dec*2019
*_WednesDAY_* *_Wednesday_*

*Play with heart...*
*Life is a beautiful game,*

*What to take if you win,*
*What did you bring if you lost?*

*Life is full of pages of memories,*

*Life is full of happy and sad events,*

*See if you sit alone and think,*

*How incomplete life is without family and friends.....*

*Take time in worship of Allah....*

*Then there will be ease in life...*

*And true life is in peace....*

*Not necessarily every gift*
*Be any object...,*
*Love, care, and*
*Respect is also a gift,*
* Give it a try....*

--------------------------------------------------
* Maintain Namaz* --------------------------------------------- ------
 * Good morning *
Thank God
